    "body": "### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.7.0-dev\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nUbuntu 20.04\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nKonsole 19.12.3\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\napt\n\n### How to reproduce the issue\n\n* run nvim with nvim-treesitter and nvim-treesitter-playground\r\n* `:set filetype=c`\r\n* `:TSPlaygroundToggle`\r\n* insert\r\n  ```c\r\n  #define FOO\r\n  #define BAR\r\n  ```\r\n* Press o (open query editor)\r\n* enter `(preproc_def)+ @test`\r\n* hover over `@test` to highlight query results\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nBoth `preproc_def` nodes get highlighted\n\n### Actual behavior\n\nOnly the last `preproc_def`node is highlighted",
